' ===================== INCLUDE / EXTEND: AUTH NOTE =====================

note bottom of UC_Login
All main system actions require
an authenticated Session.
end note

' ===================== INCLUDE / EXTEND: COURSE REGISTRATION =====================

UC_RegisterCourse ..> UC_CheckCredits : <<include>>
UC_RegisterCourse ..> UC_CheckFails : <<include>>
UC_RegisterCourse ..> UC_CheckCourseAvailability : <<include>>
UC_RegisterCourse ..> UC_CheckPrerequisites : <<include>>
UC_RegisterCourse ..> UC_CreateEnrollment : <<include>>

UC_ApproveRegistration ..> UC_ViewRegistrationStatus : <<include>>
UC_RejectRegistration ..> UC_ViewRegistrationStatus : <<include>>

' ===================== INCLUDE / EXTEND: MARKS =====================

UC_PutMark ..> UC_ValidateMark : <<include>>
UC_PutMark ..> UC_UpdateStudentRecord : <<include>>
UC_ViewTranscript ..> UC_ViewMarks : <<include>>
UC_RateTeacher ..> UC_ValidateRating : <<include>>

' ===================== INCLUDE / EXTEND: TEACHER =====================

UC_SendComplaint ..> UC_SelectUrgency : <<include>>
UC_ManageCourse ..> UC_ViewStudentsInCourse : <<include>>

' ===================== INCLUDE / EXTEND: MANAGER =====================

UC_AssignCourseTeacher ..> UC_ChooseLessonType : <<include>>
UC_ViewStudentsSorted ..> UC_SortStudents : <<include>>
UC_ViewTeachersSorted ..> UC_SortTeachers : <<include>>

