UC_NotifySubscribers ..> UC_ReceiveNotification : <<include>>

' ===================== NOTES =====================

note top of UC_RegisterCourse
Business rules:
1) Student credits must not exceed 21.
2) Student fail count must not exceed 3.
3) Course must be available.
4) Prerequisites must be satisfied.
end note

note bottom of UC_PublishPaper
Publishing a paper triggers:
- saving paper in journal
- notifying subscribers
- creating pinned research news
end note

note bottom of UC_ManageNews
Research news has higher priority
and is pinned using Decorator logic.
end note

note bottom of UC_SubscribeJournal
Journal notification follows
Observer pattern:
Journal = Subject,
User / NewsService / NotificationService = Observers.
end note

@enduml